            "body": "<p>You should get yourself familiar to the concept of <em>peer classes<\/em>.<\/p>\n\n<p>That is thoroughly described in this online book from Sun (or Oracle to be picky): <a href=\"http://java.sun.com/docs/books/jni/html/stubs.html#30234\" rel=\"nofollow\">Peer Classes<\/a>.<\/p>\n",
            "answer_id": 11879181,
            "question_id": 11876501
        },
        {
            "owner": {
                "profile_image": "https://www.gravatar.com/avatar/91386aa12420adf6a7b4145a8d9399fa?s=256&d=identicon&r=PG",
